name: Aisha Gaddafi
description: I am the epitome of a white sheep- growing up I was the weird man with his head in a book. I was a bit of a rebel man in my younger days. Now I’m on the level. I’m a free thinker, I love to learn new things. I do not judge anyone. Music is my life, I also paint as well. I love doing arts and crafts, sports and other things, i like to travel, to meet new peoples and differnce cultures.
